column1: Baby Barnaby's////I had high hopes that the chicken-fried steak & eggs combination
column2: and the green eggs plate (served with fried potatoes and chicken sausage) would mitigate the exasperating service
column3: but the food was nothing spectacular and it did not live up to all the hype. The highly acclaimed food did not make up for the overall experience as I had hoped. Just ordinary breakfast food.
